    </div>
</div>

<p>A hugely comfortable bed, intriguing art, a well-stocked bathroom and the gentle sounds of the city outside all make this a unique way to stay in Valletta. If you want an authentic experience that offers thoughtful luxury, then this beautiful place needs to be your next destination.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/casa-ellul/casa-ellul-13.jpg" alt="casa-ellul-13.jpg" /></p>

