    </div>
</div>

<p>Casa Ellul offers a 24 hr room service as well as a restaurant. Breakfast is fabulous. I am, even now, still thinking of their Eggs Benedict, freshly baked bread and fragrant coffee.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/casa-ellul/casa-ellul-30.jpg" alt="casa-ellul-30.jpg" /></p>

<div class="row no-gutters">
    <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12">
