    </div>
</div>

<p><img src="/images/malta/casa-ellul/casa-ellul-27.jpg" alt="casa-ellul-27.jpg" /></p>

<p>These are difficult times for everyone currently and sometimes we all need to take a bit of time out to review life. If, like me, you think that Life needs to be more like Art, you will find that at Casa Ellul it is.</p>

